history.text: Hello! How are you? What movie are we discussing today?
Interesting. What is the movie about? Who is in the movie?
The movie is about a news reporter that hopes to become an anchor. Jim Carey is one of the actors in the movie.
Sounds cool. I like Jim Carrey. So I guess this is a comedy?
Who else is in the movie apart from Jim Carrey?
It is a comedy. You also have Morgan Freeman and Jennifer Anniston in the movie too!
Nice. I like Freeman and Anniston too. What do they play in the movie?

Morgan Freeman plays God and Jennifer Anniston plays a woman name
d Grace Connelly.
Oh wow. Morgan Freeman is God? Sounds fun. By the way who is Bruce and why is he Almighty as the title suggests?

Yes,
 he plays God but only to give Bruce a chance to play God himself. That's where the Almighty in 'Bruce Almighty' comes from.
Could you remind me who Bruce? Is he the reporter played by Jim Carrey? That sounds even funnier!
Tell me more about the movie. What happens in the movie when Bruce plays God?
